      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'GOAL

    Serve as many customers as possible before the day ends.

    Earn
    PawCoins and get high satisfaction ratings!


    CONTROLS

    W, A, S, D or
    Arrows Keys- Move

    SHIFT - Sprint

    E - Interact with objects (like the
    Boba Station)


    HOW TO PLAY

    1. Wait for a customer to order.

    2.
    Go to the Boba Station and press E to craft their drink.

    3. Serve the drink
    before they lose patience!


    HOTKEYS

    F5 (or T) - Instantly end the day
    (Debug Mode)

    ESC - Pause the Game or go to Main Menu


    Press SPACE to
    start playing

'
